        <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank">nodejs</a>, <a href ="https://github.com/expressjs/" target="_blank">expressjs</a>, 
        <a href="https://www.postgresql.org/" target="_blank">PostgreSQL</a>. The frontend uses <a href="https://getbootstrap.com" target="_blank">Bootstrap</a>, 
