      </p>

      <p>
        <a href="https://github.com/tomjar" target="_blank">github</a> 
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/tom-reese-b47049157" target="_blank">linkedin</a>
        <a href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/24684389" target="_blank">strava</a>
